      <item>Towards the Explanation and Modelling of the Spatial and Regional Dimensions of the Transformation Process /[edited by Ryszard Domanski]. - [Poland] : Polish Academy of Sciences Committee for Space Economy and Regional Planning, 1996.</item>
      <item>The Spatial Transformation of the Economy /[edited by Ryszard Domanski]. - [Poland] : Polish Academy of Sciences Committee for Space Economy and Regional Planning, 1998.</item>
      <item>Emerging Spatial and Regional Structures of an Economy in Transition /[edited by Ryszard Domanski]. - [Poland] : Polish Academy of Sciences Committee for Space Economy and Regional Planning, 1998.</item>
      <item>The Competitiveness of Regions in the Polish and European Perspective /[edited by Ryszard Domanski]. - [Poland] : Polish Academy of Sciences Committee for Space Economy and Regional Planning, 1999.</item>
