      <item>Polycentric Metropolitan Regions - New Concepts and Experiences /[edited by Tadeusz Markowski and Tadeusz Marszal]. - [Poland] : Polish Academy of Sciences Committee for Space Economy and Regional Planning, 2002.</item>
